author: bjarkler
message:
test(core): create ivy-trusted-types integration test (#39614)

Create an integration test for testing support for Trusted Types in Ivy.
Generated with:

```
yarn ng new ivy-trusted-types -g --skip-install --style css --routing --strict
```

PR Close #39614
